@NODE INSTALLATION "INSTALLATION"
Harddisk

Copy the drawer `Amatrix` where you want and start with dobbleklick.

Disk

Format a disk and copy the drawer `Amatrix` to the disk. Start Amiga with
Workbench-Disk and start Amatrix with dobbleklick.

@ENDNODE

@NODE System_requirements "System requirements"
Amatrix should work an any Amiga. A fast processor is nice but not
necessary.

